name: Mask Coffee Table
description: The Mask Coffee Table by Kifu Paris is a versatile and organic piece. The amorphous top and base are inlaid in a mixture of shagreen, white quartz or shell and bronze-patina brass. This piece is designed by Kifu Augousti, the daughter of Ria and Yiouri Augousti. Available as a nesting side table and a coffee table. Currently made to order with an 8-10 week production time. Design SKU reference KCF06. Custom color/sizing available on request.
